title: Bakari Sellers Interview and More
itunes:title: Bakari Sellers Interview and More
description:
Today on the show we had friend to the room Bakari Sellers stop by where he spoke about Biden & Harris' first year in office, vasectomies, ancestry education and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a woman who stuffed her kid in the trunk because he had Covid and Angela helped a listener out who was struggling working with his ex about getting their kids vaccinated.
